subSubSection.paragraph:
Measurements of setae and shields of females from Serra do Cipó agree well with those informed in the literature, with the exception of the dimensions of setae Z4 , Z5 and S5 , which are shorter. In particular, setae Z5 are noticeably shorter, not exceeding 50 µm, while other authors reported lengths between 63–80 µm (
Cavalcante et al . 2017
;
Kreiter et al . 2018
).
